D. Acquisition Strategy
The program office awarded two competitive Engineering and Manufacturing Development (EMD) contracts to two vendors to build 16 vehicles each (32 total). The
program entered the acquisition cycle at Milestone B in FY 2016 and down-selected to one vendor at Milestone C in the 3rd quarter of FY 2018; the program entered
Low-Rate Initial Production (LRIP) at Milestone C with approval for two Lots of LRIP.



