A. Mission Description and Budget Item Justification
This project is a Congressional addition in FY 2024 to determine whether Spherical Brakes would be a suitable replacement for the existing brake system on the ACV
Family of Vehicles. It includes developing the Engineering Change Proposal (ECP) for Spherical Brakes with the Army Rapid Capabilities and Critical Technologies
Office (RCCTO) and Reliability Qualification Testing (RQT) and Mission Profile Testing with the Aberdeen Test Center. The Army RCCTO executes rapid prototyping
and initial equipping of strategically important capabilities to meet commanders' warfighting needs.

