to both systems. Continue development of the Actively Steered Electronic Array (AESA), an antenna providing simultaneous transmit and receive capability across a
broad frequency range with high Effective Isotropic Radiated Power (EIRP) and gain-to-noise temperature. Begin development of a new High Frequency (HF) Direction


