- Will continue to research, develop, integrate and test capabilities for sensing (passive and active) enemy activity within the
electromagnetic spectrum and jamming effectiveness, Low Probability of Intercept/Detection (LPI/LPD), Small UAS comm relay
systems, ground-based SEAD, and any other emerging ST requirements.
- Will continue to study requirements to address future capability gaps.
