       In FY 2024, the budget increased by 19.585 million due to a Congressional directed transfer from RDT&E, AF, PE 0601102F, Defense Research Sciences, for
       space unique S&T.

       Current change statement represents the decrease from FY2025 in the value of 0.550K from the previous PB.

