Description: B-21 Raider will be a dual-capable penetrating strike stealth bomber capable of delivering both
conventional and nuclear munitions. Designed to operate in tomorrow's high-end threat environment, the B-21
will play a critical role in ensuring America's enduring airpower capability.

FY 2026 Plans:
FY 2026 includes funding for the continuation of modernization studies/ technical risk reduction activities. In
addition, modernization activities will be supported, which includes but is not limited to, weapon integration/
certification, air vehicle provisioning for future capabilities, sensors, and payloads.
FY 2027 Base Plans:
FY 2027 includes funding for the continuation of modernization studies/ technical risk reduction activities. In
addition, modernization activities will be supported, which includes but is not limited to, weapons integration/
certification, air vehicle provisioning for future capabilities, sensors, and payloads.
