D. Acquisition Strategy
The B-21 philosophy to drive success has been to actively manage the program, contract and contractor; to partner with the prime and supply chain for win-win
successes; and to aggressively identify and mitigate risk early. The acquisition strategy incentivizes industry partners to achieve cost, schedule and performance
objectives.




