Mature ESS ground framework and integration prototype, Ground Integration and Framework (GIF), System of Systems
Integration (SoSI). The GIF/SoSI vendor will define and develop the Ground Assembly, Integration, and Test (Ground AI&T)
minimum viable product (MVP) and run the integration test with all ESS vendors and system capability in FY 2026, with a
