terminal, and ground framework segments. The Mission Planning prototype will then begin integrating with operational users
at operational locations and building test and training applications with the GIF/SoSI vendor. All integration issues found during
Ground AI&T testing will be fixed in FY 2026 in an agile ramp up to ensure software is mission capable upon exit of Ground AI&T
in FY 2027.

